{"tid":318163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【茶記爆炸】一人嚴重燒傷　消防：對面街車房亦受波及","createTime":"2017-07-12T02:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T04:53:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93c50c91a4fa9ea2acd2d9899c13784835aa21b9","tid":318163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499819399_1d67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170712%2Flarge%2F1499819399_1d67.jpg&h=9797f4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣長寧街35號一間茶餐廳今早發生氣體爆炸，4人受傷。消防九龍西助理消防區長黃炳權表示，消防於今晨6時33分接報，4分鐘到場後現場沒有出現明火，同時發現四人受傷，包括兩名職員及兩名食客，其中一人傷勢嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n單位面積約5米乘10米，出動13輛消防車及7輛救護車到場。而由於爆炸威力極大，單位嚴重損毀，餐廳外四輛停泊的汽車及對面一間車房亦受波及。<br />\n<br />\n黃炳權表示，餐廳使用樽裝石油氣，並引述職員指是開爐時發生爆炸，確實原因仍需要調查，消防同時在現場搬出兩個、每個重15公斤的樽裝石油氣樽，氣樽沒有損毀，會聯同機電署調查事故起因，並已通知屋宇署，而餐廳樓上單位毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499819961_657c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170712%2Flarge%2F1499819961_657c.jpg&h=45f5ffd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆炸衝擊令不少物品飛向對面街，車房大門鐵閘凹陷，門口滿地碎片。(黃江奇攝)"},{"pid":"08fa2df6037eca35752b70434cf0dc7622b6df4f","tid":318163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56944412&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56944412%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170712&d=6NW41eiVfPN9Fm6qWJyIpxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f362e7a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56944412%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170712&h=2257e327\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56944412&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170712</a>"},{"pid":"82c843947481026fb1fc18e0bb27e22ef9dd59bc","tid":318163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aeb30f7fa3971592d4fe8c8551ef67c3af51a4","tid":318163,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"炸到咁<br />\n入面d人咪個個內傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218733d672252e7f093730a15db7842b51e04533","tid":318163,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d6ff374284662dc6bb15840210deacd54b680b","tid":318163,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ce81bf9d1d5bf125ecfc3f5870342d84fcda42","tid":318163,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4d8c293cb019d2ef3bfcd57ad6986a2fbc6f483","tid":318163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c178ae1a417ce1a77232a2bb08fbc4262c6e999","tid":318163,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e3ff1208ee4cf132d4f95a56bac48ac509a56e1","tid":318163,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"9成燒傷個個人可能會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcd216d1594d9ab0e254fc308baa84279d02e75","tid":318163,"u